  <brief_title>Computer-Assisted Total Knee Replacement Kinematics: DePuy Sigma Posterior Cruciate Substituting Knee and the DePuy Sigma RP Rotating Platform Knee</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Investigation of Computer-Assisted Total Knee Replacement Kinematics on Patient Performance: An Examination of the DePuy P.F.C.速 SigmaTM Posterior Cruciate Substituting Knee and the DePuy P.F.C.速 Sigma RP Rotating Platform Knee Systems</official_title>
